race.description: Heat Of The Rising Star Handicap
race.comment: Hard to put a pen through any of these. Ended up with ALL ABOUT ARTIE (1) who started favourite but found one better when resuming over 1310m at Lismore last start, his fifth straight minor placing. Maps nicely from the good gate over a slightly longer trip. Sure to play a significant role again. SHE'S ENUFF (10) ran a decent race here first-up then needed more ground last time when run off her legs over 1110m at Lismore. Draws a good gate and is far better placed out to this distance so she can improve sharply. GAMING (8) chimed in late to finish third in a similar race here two runs back that has thrown up three subsequent winners. Followed that up with a nice third at Lismore last start. One of the better chances again. HYPOTHERMIA (7) was back in form last start in a Class 2 here. Saves her best for Grafton so stick with her. Market watch on ROYAL VICTORY (2) first-up from a spell and a switch from Phillip Stokes to Stephen Lee.
